name: KAREEM'S PAGE.
description:
This is what Kareem wrote for me.
As you can see his writing isn't great. I texted his dad, Christopher, to see if he could help me make out what Kareem wrote. Christopher explained to me that Kareem's handwriting gets like that when he's very nervous. He asked Kareem what the writing was supposed to say and Kareem said it was meant to say "something about his love for football".
